*Pokazati* mu je šta se dogodilo. (Show him what happened.)
Kako bi se *pokazalo*, ispostavilo se da je ona u pravu. (As it turned out, it showed that she was right.)
Trebalo je da *pokažu* da su sposobni da obave posao. (They had to show that they are capable to do the job.)
Neki su se ljudi odlučili da *pokažu* svoju lojalnost i podršku. (Some people decided to show their loyalty and support.)
Njegovo izlaganje je *pokazalo* da je on dobro obučen. (His presentation showed that he was well-trained.)